author: dblevins
msg: use a backup strategy for finding xml files in the event that xbean-finder getResourceMap is unable to find the descriptors.  This will happen if the jar archive was created without any directory entries.  Rare, but is valid.  In such archives 'WEB-INF/beans.xml' will exist but 'WEB-INF/' will not.
